               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Homily by Theodotus of Ancyra on the commemoration of St George, for
                     the 23th of Miyāzyā (fols. 4ra-15rb) 
 - Introduction (fols. 4ra-7rb, l.21)
                     
 - Discourse on the origin of the genealogy of St George (fols. 7rb,
                     l.21-15rb, l.3) 
 II) Gadla Giyorgis “Vita of George” (fols. 15rb,
                     l.3-93rb, l.6) 
 III) Taʾammǝra Giyorgis “Miracles of George”: 12 miracles
                     (fols. 93ra, l.7-108va) 
 - Introduction (fols. 93ra, l.6-96va, l.14)
                     
 Additio 1.</summary>
