                              ፮ለኅዳር: <locus target="#55r">fol. 55r</locus>. ዘታኅሣሥ፡ አንብብ: <locus target="#62r">fol. 62r</locus>. ዘጥር፡ ምንባብ: <locus target="#68r">fol. 68r</locus>. ዘየካቲት: <locus target="#77r">fol. 77r</locus>.
